---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Koleksi Buku Sekolah Digital">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-700 mb-4 text-center">Koleksi Buku Sekolah Digital</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">Berikut adalah kumpulan buku pelajaran digital SD, SMP, dan SMA yang dapat diakses secara gratis untuk menunjang pembelajaran formal di sekolah.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Contoh Buku SD -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-blue-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-sd-tema1.jpg" alt="Buku SD Tema 1" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2 text-center">Buku Tematik SD Kelas 1 Tema 1</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Diriku - Buku Tematik Terpadu Kurikulum 2013</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1f-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-blue-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Contoh Buku SMP -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-green-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-smp-ipa.jpg" alt="Buku SMP IPA" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-green-700 mb-2 text-center">Buku IPA SMP Kelas 7</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam - Kurikulum 2013</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1g-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-green-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Contoh Buku SMA -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-purple-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-sma-matematika.jpg" alt="Buku SMA Matematika" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2 text-center">Buku Matematika SMA Kelas 10</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Matematika Wajib - Kurikulum 2013</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1h-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-purple-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">* Semua buku diambil dari sumber resmi Kemdikbud dan dapat diakses secara legal.</div>
  </section>
</Layout>
